 November 2011\n|time=16:00\n|team1=[[S.C. Beira-Mar|Beira-Mar]]\n|score=  1\u20132 \n|report= [http://www.lpfp.pt/bwincup/pages/jogo.aspx?epoca=20112012&jornada=5&jogo=7298 Report]\n|team2= [[Moreirense F.C.|Moreirense]] \n|goals1= [[Douglas de Oliveira|Douglas]] {{goal|49}} \n|goals2= {{ubl|[[Pintassilgo (footballer)|Pintassilgo]] {{goal|76}} | [[W\u00e1gner de Andrade Borges|W\u00e1gner]] {{goal|90}}}}\n|stadium=[[Est\u00e1dio Municipal de Aveiro]], [[Aveiro, Portugal|Aveiro]], [[Portugal]]\n|attendance= 683\n|referee= Vasco Santos}}\n''Moreirense won 4-3 on aggregate.\n----\n{{footballbox\n|id = Mar\u00edtimo v Uni\u00e3o da Madeira\n|date=12 November 2011\n|time=16:00\n|team1=[[C.S. Mar\u00edtimo|Mar\u00edtimo]]\n|score= 2\u20130 \n|report= [http://www.lpfp.pt/bwincup/pages/jogo.aspx?epoca=20112012&jornada=5&jogo=7301 Report]\n|team2= [[C.F. Uni\u00e3o|Uni\u00e3o da Madeira]] \n|goals1= {{ubl|[[Jo\u00e3o Guilherme]] {{goal|79}} | [[Baba Diawara|Diawara]] {{goal|87}}}}\n|goals2=\n|stadium=[[Est\u00e1dio dos Barreiros]], [[Funchal]], [[Portugal]]\n|attendance= 1,832\n|referee= Bruno Esteves}}\n''Mar\u00edtimo won 5-2 on aggregate. \n----\n{{footballbox\n|id = Gil Vicente v Belenenses\n|date=12 November 2011\n|time=20:15\n|team1=[[Gil Vicente F.C.|Gil Vicente]]\n|score= 2\u20130\n|report= [http://www.lpfp.pt/bwincup/pages/jogo.aspx?epoca=20112012&jornada=5&jogo=7297 Report]\n|team2= [[C.F. Os Belenenses|Belenenses]] \n|goals1= {{ubl|[[Cl\u00e1udio Carolino|Cl\u00e1udio]] {{goal|51}} | [[Lu\u00eds Carlos Lima|Lu\u00eds Carlos]] {{goal|57}}}}\n|goals2=\n|stadium=[[Est\u00e1dio Cidade de Barcelos]], [[Barcelos, Portugal|Barcelos]], [[Portugal]]\n|attendance= 3,964\n|referee= Rui Costa}}\n''Gil Vicenre won 3-2 on aggregate.''\n----\n{{footballbox\n|id = Uni\u00e3o de Leiria v Santa Clara\n|date=13 November 2011\n|time=16:00\n|team1= [[U.D. Leiria|Uni\u00e3o de Leiria]]\n|score= 1\u20130\n|report= [http://www.lpfp.pt/bwincup/pages/jogo.aspx?epoca=20112012&jornada=5&jogo=7296 Report]\n|team2= [[C.D. Santa Clara|Santa Clara]]\n|goals1= [[Bruno Moraes|Moraes]] {{goal|53|pen.}}\n|goals2=\n|stadium=[[Municipal da Marinha Grande]], [[Marinha Grande Municipality|Marinha Grande]], [[Portugal]]\n|attendance= 473\n|referee= Cosme Cunha Machado\n}}\n''Santa Clara won 3-2 on aggregate.\n----\n{{footballbox\n|id = Acad\u00e9mica v Penafiel\n|date=13 November 2011\n|time=19:15\n|team1=[[Associa\u00e7\u00e3o Acad\u00e9mica de Coimbra \u2013 O.A.F.|Acad\u00e9mica]]\n|score= 0\u20131\n|report= [http://www.lpfp.pt/bwincup/pages/jogo.aspx?epoca=20112012&jornada=5&jogo=7294 Report]\n|team2=[[F.C. Penafiel|Penafiel]] \n|goals1=\n|goals2= [[Manoel Cristiano Ribeiro Lemes|Manoel]] {{goal|46}}\n|stadium=[[Est\u00e1dio Cidade de Coimbra]], [[Coimbra]], [[Portugal]]\n|attendance= 524\n|referee= Paulo Baptista\n}}\n''Penafiel won 2-1 on aggregate.\n\n==Third round==\nThe 2011\u201312 Ta\u00e7a da Liga Third Round group stage matches are to be played in January and February 2012. The eight winners of the two legged Second Round matches progressed to this round and are joined by the teams who finished in the top eight of the 2010\u201311 Primeira Liga. The sixteen teams will be seeded depending on their league position from the previous season. The sixteen teams involved in this round would be split into four groups from group A to D.  The first round matches of the group stage took place on 21 December 2011 and 2\u20133 January 2012, the second-round games took place on 18 January and the third round matches took place on 2\u20133 February 2012.<ref>{{cite news|title=BWIN CUP - 2011/2012 - 3.\u00aa FASE|trans-title=2011-12 - Bwin Cup - Third Round|language=Portuguese|url=http://www.abola.pt/nacional/tliga.aspx|accessdate=27 November 2011|date=27 November 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111126181438/http://www.abola.pt/nacional/tliga.aspx|archive-date=26 November 2011|url-status=dead|df=dmy-all}}</ref> The winners of each group would progress to the semi final stage to be played on the 21 March 2012.\n\n===Participating teams===\nNames in '''bold''' are the colloquial names of the clubs. [[G.D. Estoril-Praia|Estoril]], [[Gil Vicente F.C.|Gil Vicente]], [[C.S. Mar\u00edtimo|Mar\u00edtimo]], [[Moreirense F.C.|Moreirense]], [[F.C. Penafiel|Penafiel]], [[Portimonense S.C. (football team)|Portimonense]], [[C.D. Santa Clara|Santa Clara]], [[Vit\u00f3ria F.C.|Vit\u00f3ria de Set\u00fabal]] all progressed from the [[2011\u201312 Ta\u00e7a da Liga (Second Round)|Second Round]] to this phase. [[S.L. Benfica|Benfica]], [[C.D. Nacional|Nacional]], [[F.C. Pa\u00e7os de Ferreira|Pa\u00e7os de Ferreira]], [[FC Porto|Porto]], [[Rio Ave F.C.|Rio Ave]], [[Sporting Clube de Portugal|Sporting CP]], [[S.C. Braga|Braga]] and [[Vit\u00f3ria S.C.|Vit\u00f3ria de Guimar\u00e3es]] started their campaign at this stage.\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n* [[S.L. Benfica|Sport Lisboa e '''Benfica''']]\n* [[G.D. Estoril-Praia|Grupo Desportivo '''Estoril-Praia''']]\n* [[Gil Vicente F.C.|'''Gil Vicente''' Futebol Clube]]\n* [[C.S. Mar\u00edtimo|Club Sport '''Mar\u00edtimo''']]\n* [[Moreirense F.C.|'''Moreirense''' Futebol Clube]]\n* [[C.D. Nacional|Clube Desportivo '''Nacional''']] \"'''da Madeira'''\"\n* [[F.C. Pa\u00e7os de Ferreira|Futebol Clube '''Pa\u00e7os de Ferreira''']]\n* [[F.C. Penafiel|Futebol Clube de '''Penafiel''']]\n{{col-2}}\n* [[Portimonense S.C. (football team)|'''Portimonense''' Sporting Clube]]\n* [[FC Porto|Futebol Clube do '''Porto''']]\n* [[Rio Ave Futebol Clube|'''Rio Ave''' Futebol Clube]]\n* [[C.D. Santa Clara|Clube Desportivo '''Santa Clara''']]\n* [[Sporting Clube de Portugal|'''Sporting''' Clube de Portugal]]\n* [[S.C. Braga|Sporting Clube de '''Braga''']]\n* [[Vit\u00f3ria S.C.|'''Vit\u00f3ria''' Sport Clube]] \"'''de Guimar\u00e3es'''\"\n* [[Vit\u00f3ria F.C.|'''Vit\u00f3ria''' Futebol Clube]] \"'''de Set\u00fabal'''\"\n{{col-end}}\n\n===Draw===\nThe draw for the Third Round took place on 23 November 2012 at 12:00 at the [[Portuguese League for Professional Football|LPFP]] headquarters in [[Lisbon]], [[Portugal]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Sorteio da terceira fase da bwin cup |trans-title=Draw for the Third Round of the Bwin Cup|language=Portuguese|url=http://www.lpfp.pt/Pages/Sorteiodaterceirafasedabwincup.aspx|accessdate=22 November 2011|date=22 November 2011}}</ref> The teams involved in this round were seeded according to their league position from either the [[2010\u201311 Primeira Liga]] or the [[2010\u201311 Liga de Honra]] depending in which division they played in last season.<ref>{{cite news|title=Sorteio da 3.\u00aa fase|trans-title=Third Round Draw|language=Portuguese|url=http://www.abola.pt/nnh/ver.aspx?id=300333|accessdate=23 November 2011|date=23 November 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111125181220/http://www.abola.pt/nnh/ver.aspx?id=300333|archive-date=25 November 2011|url-status=dead|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" width=98%\n|-\n!width=25%| Pot 1 \n!width=25%| Pot 2 \n!width=25%| Pot 3 \n!width=25%| Pot 4 \n|- \n| valign=\"top\"|\n*[[FC Porto|Porto]]\n*[[S.L. Benfica|Benfica]]\n*[[Sporting Clube de Portugal|Sporting CP]]\n*[[S.C. Braga|Braga]]\n| valign=\"top\"|\n*[[Vit\u00f3ria S.C.|Vit\u00f3ria de Guimar\u00e3es]]\n*[[C.D. Nacional|Nacional]]\n*[[F.C. Pa\u00e7os de Ferreira|Pa\u00e7os de Ferreira]]\n*[[Rio Ave F.C.|Rio Ave]]\n| valign=\"top\"|\n*[[C.S. Mar\u00edtimo|Mar\u00edtimo]]\n*[[Vit\u00f3ria F.C.|Vit\u00f3ria de Set\u00fabal]]\n*[[Portimonense S.C. (football team)|Portimonense]]\n*[[Gil Vicente F.C.|Gil Vicente]]\n| valign=\"top\"|\n*[[Moreirense F.C.|Moreirense]]\n*[[C.D. Santa Clara|Santa Clara]]\n*[[G.D. Estoril Praia|Estoril]]\n*[[F.C. Penafiel|Penafiel]]\n|}\n\n===Groups===\n\n====Group A====\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=Q\n\n|team1=GVI|name_GVI=[[Gil Vicente F.C.|Gil Vicente]]\n|team2=MOR|name_MOR=[[Moreirense F.C.|Moreirense]]\n|team3=SCP|name_SCP=[[Sporting Clube de Portugal|Sporting CP