13 O.A.F.|Acad\u00e9mica]] ||1\u20131|1\u20130}}\n{{TwoLegResult| '''[[C.D. Santa Clara|Santa Clara]]''' ||3\u20132| [[U.D. Leiria|Uni\u00e3o de Leiria]] ||3\u20131|0\u20131}}\n{{TwoLegResult| [[Associa\u00e7\u00e3o Naval 1\u00ba de Maio|Naval]] ||3\u20134| '''[[Vit\u00f3ria F.C.|Vit\u00f3ria de Set\u00fabal]]''' ||1\u20132|2\u20132}}\n{{TwoLegResult| '''[[Moreirense F.C.|Moreirense]]''' ||4\u20133| [[S.C. Beira-Mar|Beira-Mar]] ||2\u20132|2\u20131}}\n{{TwoLegResult| '''[[Portimonense S.C. (football team)|Portimonense]]''' ||2\u20132(5\u20134[[Penalty shootout (football)|p]])| [[C.D. Feirense|Feirense]] ||1\u20130|1\u20132}}\n{{TwoLegResult| '''[[G.D. Estoril Praia|Estoril]]''' ||4\u20133| [[S.C. Olhanense|Olhanense]] ||4\u20133|0\u20130}}\n{{TwoLegResult| [[C.F. Os Belenenses|Belenenses]] ||2\u20133| '''[[Gil Vicente F.C.|Gil Vicente]]''' ||2\u20131|0\u20132}}\n{{end}}\n\n=== First leg ===\n{{footballbox\n|id = Uni\u00e3o da Madeira v Mar\u00edtimo\n|date=8 October 2011\n|time=16:00\n|team1=[[C.F. Uni\u00e3o|Uni\u00e3o da Madeira]] \n|score=2\u20133\n|report=[http://www.lpfp.pt/bwincup/pages/jogo.aspx?epoca=20112012&jornada=4&jogo=7293 Report]\n|team2= [[C.S. Mar\u00edtimo|Mar\u00edtimo]]\n|goals1=[[Toz\u00e9 Marreco|Marreco]] {{goal|28||61}}\n|goals2={{ubl|[[Christian Pouga|Pouga]] {{goal|21}}|[[Iorlando Pereira Marques Filho|Marquinho]] {{goal|22}}| [[Baba Diawara|Diawara]] {{goal|84}}}}\n|stadium=[[Campo do Adelino Rodrigues]], [[Funchal]], [[Portugal]]\n|attendance=1,112\n|referee= Rui Costa }}\n----\n{{footballbox\n|id = Penafiel v Acad\u00e9mica\n|date=8 October 2011\n|time=20:15\n|team1=[[F.C. Penafiel|Penafiel]] \n|score=1\u20131\n|report=[http://www.lpfp.pt/bwincup/pages/jogo.aspx?epoca=20112012&jornada=4&jogo=7286 Report]\n|team2=[[Associa\u00e7\u00e3o Acad\u00e9mica de Coimbra \u2013 O.A.F.|Acad\u00e9mica]]\n|goals1=[[El\u00edzio Albues|El\u00edzio]] {{goal|17}}\n|goals2=[[Adrien Silva|Adrien]] {{goal|90}}\n|stadium=[[Est\u00e1dio Municipal 25 de Abril]],